    <h1>Formic Attends ATX West 2025</h1>
    <div class="legal-meta">Brooklyn Kiosow, Marketing Communications Manager · Tuesday, February 11, 2025</div>
  </div>

<figure style="max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px"><img src="/articles/formic-atx-west-2025/1739295029-img_9914.jpg" alt="Formic Attends ATX West 2025" style="width:100%;height:auto;display:block" /></figure>
  <div class="legal-prose">
<p>At ATX West in Anaheim, California, last week, the Formic team met with attendees to discuss how end-of-line production automation is closing labor gaps and boosting productivity for U.S. manufacturers. As consumer demand increases, automation adoption is growing, but not every business has a big CapEx budget or the internal expertise to deploy and maintain these solutions. </p> <p>If you stopped by our ATX West booth, you saw one of our in-demand robotic palletizers on display. To make automation more accessible and easy, we introduced the Formic <a href="https://land.formic.co/full-service-palletizer-rentals">Full Service Palletizer Rental Program</a> late last year. The program includes access to four fully supported turnkey palletizing systems for one fixed monthly or annual rate. It also comes with free equipment swapping as business demands grow or change, 24/7 technical support, 100% preventative and corrective maintenance, and contracted performance rates. </p> <p>ATX was the perfect place to kick off the tradeshow season, we hope to see you next month at <a href="https://pxse25.nvytes.co/landing2025/13F15.html">PACK EXPO Southeast</a> in Atlanta, Georgia! Come enjoy a <a href="https://formic.co/stories/cameron-s-coffee-hits-automation-easy-button-scaling-from-0-to-5-systems-in-12-mo">Cameron&#x27;s Coffee</a> on us. </p> <a href="https://land.formic.co/automate-now-palletizers">Get Started with Formic Here</a>
  </div>
